race.description: Carlton Draught Harry Bell Maiden Plate
race.comment: BRAZEN WARRIOR (1) had been well educated before missing a whisker at Seymour on debut. Impressed after settling back in the field and Egan goes on today and has been aboard in trials. Will appreciate the step up in trip and can go one better. CONTOURS (2) just missed at Geelong on a heavy track on debut and that stacks right up. Meech is booked again by the premier stable and he will be finishing hard. SHADES OF STARDOM (8) was expected to win here third-up but didn't finish it off. Will likely get some cut out of the ground today, which will suit. Has the blinkers on for the first time and will go close with average luck in the run. Stablemate  FLYING DONE (5) is an improver with the blinkers on for the first time. Yendall stays aboard and will give him every chance from an inside gate.
